#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:1
msgid "E4094"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:3
msgid "Cannot modify a read-only field."
msgstr "不能修改只读字段。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:5
msgid ""
"For a read-only `struct`, you cannot modify the value of a field using "
"assignment outside of the package where the type is defined."
msgstr "对于只读结构体，您不能使用赋值在定义类型的包之外修改字段的值。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:8
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:10
msgid "Suppose you have a package `a` in module `username/hello`:"
msgstr "假设您在模块 `username/hello` 中有一个包 `a`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:12
msgid "`a/moon.pkg`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:14
msgid "\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:18
#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:43
msgid "`a/a.mbt`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:20
#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:45
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub struct T {\n"
"  mut value : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn T::new() -> T {\n"
"  T::{ value: 0 }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn T::set(self : T, value : Int) -> Unit {\n"
"  self.value = value\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:24
msgid "And you have another package `b` in the same module:"
msgstr "您在相同模块中还有另一个包 `b`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:26
msgid "`b/moon.pkg`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:28
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/E4094/a\",\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:32
#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:49
msgid "`b/b.mbt`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:34
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let a = @a.T::new()\n"
"  a.value = 3 // Error: Cannot modify a read-only field: value\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:38
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:40
msgid ""
"If you have control over the package where the type is defined, expose "
"mutation through a method in that package."
msgstr "如果您可以控制定义该类型的包，请通过该包中的方法暴露修改操作。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4094.md:51
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let a = @a.T::new()\n"
"  a.set(3)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

